channel.title: What ever happend to: Constant Tedder?
channel.description:
Hello Friends,
Today were gonna disscuse Constant Tedder, And WTF Happend to him... If you have an Idea Please post...
NO SPAMMING NO HARSH FLAMMING...You idiot this and this happend not that is O.K. :rolleyes:
Constant Tedder was one of the 3 (F)(J)agex Corp. Founders and Help Create Runescape, But Mysterouisly disappeared sometime after 2003,not officaly but just never stuck his head out the door, You know...
P.S. I searched Google and Wiki and Jagex, But got nothing besides he was a founder, which I had known... He just disappered,
My theory:
Andrew and Him got in a fight, and Paul accidently killed him and they dumped his body someplace...
